WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:15.000
舜天信兴样衣管理系统从客户会议开始：客户提出欧洲市场、轻户外、浅色系，并给出参考图。业务员直接打开业务前台找可借可推的款。
The Suntien Xinxing Sample Management System starts from a client meeting: the buyer asks for European-market, light outdoor, pale-color styles and provides a reference image.

00:15.000 --> 00:30.000
业务员用姓名、业务组和手机号登录。后续收藏、已选、PPT、借样申请和费用账单都会归到个人和业务组。
The salesperson signs in with name, team, and phone number. Favorites, selections, PPT records, loan requests, and bills are tied to that person and team.

00:30.000 --> 00:45.000
业务员按客户需求筛选设计样衣和大货样品，查看在库、季节、品类和颜色，让客户快速看到可推款。
Sales filters design and bulk samples by availability, season, category, and color so the client quickly sees pitch-ready styles.

00:45.000 --> 01:00.000
客户给参考图时，业务员点击相机上传图片，系统在可见样衣里找相似款并按匹配度排序。
When the client gives a reference, sales clicks the camera, uploads the image, and the system ranks similar visible samples.

01:00.000 --> 01:15.000
点爱心代表收藏客户感兴趣的款，勾选代表加入本次推款清单，两套状态分别服务长期关注和当前客户。
The heart favorites styles the client likes; the check mark adds items to this pitch list. The two states serve different purposes.

01:15.000 --> 01:30.000
详情页展示正面、背面、价格、借样费、尺码、库位和架杆，也推荐同品类近似款。
The detail page shows front and back images, price, loan fee, size, location, rack, and similar styles in the same category.

01:30.000 --> 01:45.000
业务员多选后点击推款 PPT，系统自动生成客户可看的推款文件，并在我的中心留下记录。
After multi-selecting styles, sales clicks Pitch PPT. The system creates a client-ready presentation and stores the record in My Center.

01:45.000 --> 02:00.000
客户想看实物时，业务员填写借用用途、预计归还时间和备注，提交借样申请到设计部后台。
When the client wants physical samples, sales fills purpose, return date, and notes, then submits a request to Design Admin.

02:00.000 --> 02:15.000
样衣管理员在后台处理申请，按库位和架杆找样衣，确认借出；归还、丢失、损坏和淘汰都有记录。
The sample admin handles the request, finds items by location and rack, confirms the loan, and records returns, loss, damage, or retirement.

02:15.000 --> 02:30.000
设计师上传正背面图，用 AI 生成白底图和补全字段，再填写价格、库位和架杆，新款入库后前台可见。
The designer uploads front and back images, uses AI for white-background images and field completion, then sets price, location, and rack.

02:30.000 --> 02:45.000
问问云知可以回答趋势、报价、汇率和在库样衣问题，把 AI 放进业务员、设计师和样衣管理员的日常工作。
Ask Yunzhi answers trends, quotes, exchange rates, and inventory questions, putting AI into daily work for sales, designers, and admins.

02:45.000 --> 03:00.000
管理层按业务组拉取周、月、年账单，分析客户和风格偏好，用数据提前准备下一季样衣。
Management pulls weekly, monthly, and yearly bills by team, analyzes client and style preferences, and prepares next-season samples from data.
